Class GameObject

java.lang.Object
game.entities.GameObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
Area, Blip, InventoryBarController, Item, MindlessAISpawner, Platform, Player, ProgressBarController, TrackedScriptedDamageZoneSpawner, TrackingAISpawner, UIController, UIElement, WallOfDeath
public abstract class GameObject
extends java.lang.Object
Superclass for all objects within the game. Contains basic important information, and enforces required functions.

      public GameObject​(float x, float y, int z, int width, int height)
      Parameters:
      x - The starting x coordinate of the object
      y - The starting y coordinate of the object
      z - The z index of the coordinate. Higher indexes are rendered on top of later indexes.
      width - The width of the object
      height - The height of the object
